l support.</span></p>\r\n<p>Most Appreciation to the Head of Mathematics Department, Professor B.I Olajuwon and the entire lecturers in the department for this opportunity.<br>My sincere appreciate to all Mathematics Student of college of physical sciences and the Executive of National Association of Mathematics Science Funaab Chapter, team Pioneer led by comrade Paul kehinde and Ademola K.T. Darasimi for making this day a reality.<br>And I also use this opportunity to welcome all fresh Mathematics Students into the prestigious Federal University of Agriculture Abeokuta, I pray that your stay be glorious and I wish you all how wonderful and fruitful semester.</p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][kc_call_to_action layout=\"3\" title=\"Meet Your Exco:apos:s\" desc=\"V2UgYXJlIHlvdXIgcmVwcmVzZW50aXZlcywgc2Nyb2xsIGRvd24gdG8ga25vdyB5b3VyIGVsZWN0ZWQgZXhlY3V0aXZlcyBhbmQgbGVhcm4gbW9yZSBob3cgd2UgY2FuIHNlcnZlIHlvdSBiZXR0ZXIu\" button_show=\"yes\" button_text=\"__empty__\" _id=\"624277\" icon_show=\"yes\" icon=\"fa-angle-double-down\"][kc_spacing height=\"12px\" _id=\"923932\"][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_spacing height=\"42px\" _id=\"638440\"][/kc_column][/kc_row][kc_row use_container=\"yes\" _id=\"800355\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" force=\"__empty__\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`background`:{`background|`:`eyJjb2xvciI6IiNmZmZmZmYiLCJsaW5lYXJHcmFkaWVudCI6WyIiXSwiaW1hZ2UiOiJub25lIiwicG9zaXRpb24iOiIwJSAwJSIsInNpemUiOiJhdXRvIiwicmVwZWF0IjoicmVwZWF0IiwiYXR0YWNobWVudCI6InNjcm9sbCIsImFkdmFuY2VkIjowfQ==`}}}}\" equal_height=\"yes\" column_align=\"middle\" _collapse=\"1\"][kc_column width=\"12/12\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"651076\"][kc_row_inner column_align=\"middle\" _id=\"147717\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" equal_height=\"yes\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"25%\" _id=\"223037\"][kc_single_image image_size=\"full\" _id=\"602540\" image_source=\"media_library\" image=\"2738\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`image-style`:{`text-align|`:`justify`}}}}\"][kc_af_tit