(1805, 1, '2021-10-19 22:14:23', '2021-10-19 22:14:23', '[kc_row use_container=\"yes\" _id=\"263020\"][kc_column width=\"12/12\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"883931\"][kc_row_inner column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"674975\"][kc_column_inner width=\"35.4%\" _id=\"334131\"][kc_spacing height=\"61px\" _id=\"66410\"][kc_single_image image_size=\"full\" _id=\"638912\" image_source=\"media_library\" image=\"1746\"][kc_af_title heading=\"3\" align=\"center\" _id=\"40404\" title=\"AKEYE SAHEED\" subtitle=\":lt:b:gt:President, COLPHYSSA:lt:/b:gt:\"][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"64.59%\" _id=\"829503\"][kc_spacing height=\"61px\" _id=\"287509\"][kc_af_title heading=\"3\" align=\"center\" _id=\"683582\" title=\"Welcome To The Official Website of the College of Physical Sciences Students Association (COLPHYSSA)\"][kc_column_text _id=\"948406\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|,p`:`justify`}}}}\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The entire students of the College of Physical Sciences of the Federal<br />University of Agriculture Abeokuta, Ogun State, Nigeria, having<br />considered the need for a body capable of fostering unity, peace and<br />protecting the interest of the cadres of Physical sciences students in<br />the University. Recognizing the need to contribute to our understanding<br />of the physical world through excellence in observation, theoretical and<br />experimental sciences and to extend quantitative, qualitative and<br />methodologies to address the problem of the school at large. In pursuit<br />of these goals, we would coordinate objectives in research, teaching and<br />infrastructure among ourselves.This Vision started 4 years ago when the<br />College Of Natural Sciences (COLNAS) was divided into College Of<br />Biological Sciences (COLBIOS) and our own <em><strong>College Of Physical Sciences (COLPHYS)</strong></em>.</p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][kc_spacing height=\"12px\" _id=\"720749\"][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row