l-sm-8\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1777200\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h3 class=\"af-heading\">Welcome To The Official Website of the College of Physical Sciences Students Association (COLPHYSSA)</h3>\r\n	</div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3476587 kc_text_block\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The entire students of the College of Physical Sciences of the Federal<br />University of Agriculture Abeokuta, Ogun State, Nigeria, having<br />considered the need for a body capable of fostering unity, peace and<br />protecting the interest of the cadres of Physical sciences students in<br />the University. Recognizing the need to contribute to our understanding<br />of the physical world through excellence in observation, theoretical and<br />experimental sciences and to extend quantitative, qualitative and<br />methodologies to address the problem of the school at large. In pursuit<br />of these goals, we would coordinate objectives in research, teaching and<br />infrastructure among ourselves.This Vision started 4 years ago when the<br />College Of Natural Sciences (COLNAS) was divided into College Of<br />Biological Sciences (COLBIOS) and our own <em><strong>College Of Physical Sciences (COLPHYS)</strong></em>.</p>\n</div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2412926\" style=\"height: 12px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2121766\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-683712 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-717789 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1585381 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>Meet Your Executives</h2><div class=\"kc-cta-text\">We are your