(1780, 1, '2021-10-19 22:12:36', '2021-10-19 22:12:36', '[kc_row use_container=\"yes\" _id=\"734700\"][kc_column width=\"12/12\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"572973\"][kc_row_inner column_align=\"middle\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"206132\"][kc_column_inner width=\"35.4%\" _id=\"800866\"][kc_spacing height=\"61px\" _id=\"806397\"][kc_single_image image_size=\"full\" _id=\"454011\" image_source=\"media_library\" image=\"1746\"][kc_af_title heading=\"3\" align=\"center\" _id=\"495745\" title=\"AKEYE SAHEED\" subtitle=\":lt:b:gt:President, COLPHYSSA:lt:/b:gt:\"][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"64.59%\" _id=\"266358\"][kc_spacing height=\"61px\" _id=\"981145\"][kc_af_title heading=\"3\" align=\"center\" _id=\"42816\" title=\"Welcome To The Official Website of the College of Physical Sciences Students Association (COLPHYSSA)\"][kc_column_text _id=\"459786\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|,p`:`justify`}}}}\"]<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The entire students of the College of Physical Sciences of the Federal<br />\nUniversity of Agriculture Abeokuta, Ogun State, Nigeria, having<br />\nconsidered the need for a body capable of fostering unity, peace and<br />\nprotecting the interest of the cadres of Physical sciences students in<br />\nthe University. Recognizing the need to contribute to our understanding<br />\nof the physical world through excellence in observation, theoretical and<br />\nexperimental sciences and to extend quantitative, qualitative and<br />\nmethodologies to address the problem of the school at large. In pursuit<br />\nof these goals, we would coordinate objectives in research, teaching and<br />\ninfrastructure among ourselves.This Vision started 4 years ago when the<br />\nCollege Of Natural Sciences (COLNAS) was divided into College Of<br />\nBiological Sciences (COLBIOS) and our own <em><strong>College Of Physical Sciences (COLPHYS)</strong></em>.</p>\n[/kc_column_text][kc_spacing height=\"12px\" _id=\"755649\"][/kc