401306 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\">	<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text owl-carousel text-center\" data-speed=\"7000\">\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Federal-University-of-Agriculture-Abeokuta-FUNAAB-1-1024x384-1.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Welcome to the Federal University of Agriculture, Abeokuta</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">National Association of Mathematics Students of Nigeria Web Page</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/math-2-1024x576-1.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Math is the Queen of Science and Arithmetic, the Queen of Maths </h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">This is the best path to thread</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/math1-3-1024x576-1.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">The Executives welcome you back on Campus!</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">We are your representives, we are here for you!</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1359630 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1174880 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2405716 kc_row kc_row_inner\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1552710 kc_col-sm-4 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-4\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-662783\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-4008585 kc_shortcode kc_single_image\">\n\n        <img src=\"http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/math.png\" class=\"\" alt=\"\" />    </div>\n<div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h4 class=\"af-heading\">OLASOJI Kolawole</h4>\r\n	<p>President, NAMSN</p></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3343423 kc_col-sm-8 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-8\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3656613\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h3 class=\"af-heading\">Welcome to the National Association of Mathematics Students of Nigeria (NAMSN) FUNAAB Chapter.</h3>\r\n	</div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2613522 kc_text_block\"><p>\n<span style=\"color: #484848; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">With a heart of appreciation do I thank the leadership of College of Physical Sciences lead by Comrade Akeye Saheed and his hard-working team (Synergy) for the resuscitation of the College website and also appreciation to the Dean of College of Physical Sciences for his full support.</span></p>\n<p>Most Appreciation to the Head of Mathematics Department, Professor B.I Olajuwon and the entire lecturers in the department for this opportunity.<br />My sincere appreciate to all Mathematics Student of college of physical sciences and the Executive of National Association of Mathematics Science Funaab Chapter, team Pioneer led by comrade Paul kehinde and Ademola K.T. Darasimi for making this day a reality.<br />And I also use this opportunity to welcome all fresh Mathematics Students into the prestigious Federal University of Agriculture Abeokuta, I pray that your stay be glorious and I wish you all how wonderful and fruitful semester.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1564673 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-3 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div cla