n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Welcome to the Federal University of Agriculture, Abeokuta</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Nigerian Association of Physics Students Web Page</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/physicss-1-1024x576-1.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">All Science is either Physics or stamp collecting</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">We do not fail unless we stop trying!</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/phy.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Your executives welcome you back on Campus</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">We are your representatives, we are here for you!</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-590484 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3914076 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-118606 kc_row kc_row_inner\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1470220 kc_col-sm-4 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-4\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2150287\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3165460 kc_shortcode kc_single_image\">\n\n        <img src=\"http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/woocommerce-placeholder-255x300-1.png\" class=\"\" alt=\"\" />    </div>\n<div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h4 class=\"af-heading\">Makanjuola Yusuf</h4>\r\n	<p>President, NAPS</p></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-4356104 kc_col-sm-8 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-8\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-534890\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h3 class=\"af-heading\">Welcome to Nigerian Association of Physics Students (NAPS) FUNAAB Chapter.</h3>\r\n	</div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2640035 kc_text_block\"><p>\n<span style=\"color: #484848; font-family: Open Sans, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hello and welcome my fellow physicists, this is the section for the study of natural phenomenon (physics). Here, You can make payment for your NAPS due, get past questions, get relevant information, get reading materials, get in touch with our executives and so much more. There is so much to learn, you can&#039;t do it alone, ask for help, go to tutorials, ask questions especially in class. Physics is around us and can be used in many applications like Engineering, Medicine, Education, Communication, even the business sector . Get to know it and then find your interests in any field you wish to go into. We are built from determination, grit and a need to thrive! Keep that fire  burning! Be prayerful! And be ready to forge a champion in you. Remember, never give up, keep pushing and strive, quitting is not the answer. May the F=MA be with you.  #team erudites</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1210736 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>Meet Your Exco&#039;s</h2><div class=\"kc-cta-text\">We are your representives, scroll down to know your elected executives and learn more how we can serve you better.</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1143516\" style=\"height: 12px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1782521\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-kc-fullwidth=\"row\" data-kc-parallax=\"true\" class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2904263 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2108030 kc_col-sm-4 kc_column kc_col-sm-4\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-197857\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-605529 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>NAPS Fresher/D.E Due Payment</h2><div class=\"kc-cta-text\">All jambites, pre-degrees, JUPEB and direct entry students are required to pay their association dues as  members of the Nigeria Association of Physics Students (NAPS), Federal University of Agriculture Abeokuta Chapter for the benefit of all.</div></div><div class=\"kc-cta-button\"><a href=\"https://www.colphyssa.com/naps-fresher/\" title=\"Fresher\">Pay Now</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1147720\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3753103 kc_col-sm-4 kc_column kc_col-sm-4\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3317989\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1627664 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>NAPS 200-300 Level Due Payment</h2><div class=\"kc-cta-text\">All Stalites; 200 level, 300 evel, and 400 level students are required to pay their association dues as  members of the Nigeria Association of Physics Students (NAPS), Federal University of Agriculture Abeokuta Chapter for the benefit of all.</div></div><div class=\"kc-cta-button\"><a href=\"https://www.colphyssa.com/naps-stalites/\" title=\"200-300L\">Pay Now</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1517730\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2340565 kc_col-sm-4 kc_column kc_col-sm-4\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1243965\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div>\n<