tion\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Welcome to the Federal  University of Agriculture, Abeokuta</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Association of Statistics Students of Nigeria</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/statt-2-1024x576-1.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">Statistics is the Grammar of Science</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">This is the best path to thread!</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n								<div class=\"af-slider-bg-text-item\" style=\"background-image:url(http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/stat-2-1024x576-1.jpg)\">\r\n				<div class=\"af-title af-slider-bg-text-caption\">\r\n					<h2 class=\"h1-size\" style=\"color:#ffffff;\">The Executives welcome you back on Campus</h2>					<p style=\"color:#ffffff;\">We are your representatives, we are here for you!</p>				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2442906 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2132889 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1309052 kc_row kc_row_inner\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-512095 kc_col-sm-4 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-4\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3056424\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1053584 kc_shortcode kc_single_image\">\n\n        <img src=\"http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/woocommerce-placeholder-255x300-1.png\" class=\"\" alt=\"\" />    </div>\n<div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h4 class=\"af-heading\">Olaogun Adenike</h4>\r\n	<p>President, ASSON</p></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3500866 kc_col-sm-8 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-8\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1085058\" style=\"height: 61px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div><div class=\"af-title text-center\">\r\n	<h3 class=\"af-heading\">Welcome to the Association of Statistics Students of Nigeria (ASSON) FUNAAB Chapter.</h3>\r\n	</div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3757995 kc_text_block\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #484848; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">It is my pleasure to welcome you all on this platform. I am delighted that the Presiding officer of the College in person of Comrade Joseph ONI and his Directors indulge this medium. I also wish to appreciate all ASSONITES for complimenting my intention to serve as the President (ASSON FUNAAB) for this Academy year(19/20).Over the years, COLPHYS has been known to always spring forth her uniqueness in all dimension; say academics, talents, growth, achievements...  A legacy which you and I should live by.<br />\nI take this opportunity to implore that as you walk throughout the Academy year(s), you should talk about, reflect and act on the meaning of diligence, excellence, integrity and inclusion. From interacting as you have brought your passion and energy back to school, I hope that everyone will see those four key words as guiding principles that we should strive to uphold in all that we do because these are the fundamental beliefs that will continue to define us and provide a strong sense of who we are as a student and distinct us collectively as COLPHYSSITES.<br />\nI must also add that theres a need for us to discover and always consider what your core values are relating it to your everyday thoughts, actions and what we spend most of the time on to know if we really have to reframe our decisions and hold ourselves accountable. I believe SUCCESS IS WHAT EVERYONE CAN ATTAIN.</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3898075 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>Meet Your Exco&#039;s</h2><div class=\"kc-cta-text\">We are your representives, scroll down to know your elected executives and learn more how we can serve you better.</div></div><div class=\"kc-cta-button\"><a href=\"#\">Scroll Down <span class=\"kc-cta-icon\"><i class=\"fa-angle-double-down\"></i></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1758433\" style=\"height: 12px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-688207\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-kc-fullwidth=\"row\" data-kc-parallax=\"true\" class=\"kc-elm kc-css-262678 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-295850 kc_col-sm-6 kc_column kc_col-sm-6\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3329832\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2171445 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>ASSON Fresher/D.E Due Payment</h2><div class=\"kc-cta-text\">All jambites, pre-degrees, JUPEB and direct entry students are required to pay their association dues as  members of the Association of Statistics Students of Nigeria (ASSON), Federal University of Agriculture Abeokuta Chapter for the benefits of all.</div></div><div class=\"kc-cta-button\"><a href=\"https://www.colphyssa.com/payment/\" title=\"Fresher\">Pay Now</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-903043\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-4178360 kc_col-sm-6 kc_column kc_col-sm-6\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2550723\" style=\"height: 42px; clear: both; width:100%;\"></div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3919037 kc-call-to-action kc-cta-2 kc-is-button\">\n\n	<div class=\"kc-cta-desc\"><h2>ASSON Stalites 