to serve as the President (ASSON FUNAAB) for this Academy year(19/20).Over the years, COLPHYS has been known to always spring forth her uniqueness in all dimension; say academics, talents, growth, achievements...  A legacy which you and I should live by.<br />\r\nI take this opportunity to implore that as you walk throughout the Academy year(s), you should talk about, reflect and act on the meaning of diligence, excellence, integrity and inclusion. From interacting as you have brought your passion and energy back to school, I hope that everyone will see those four key words as guiding principles that we should strive to uphold in all that we do because these are the fundamental beliefs that will continue to define us and provide a strong sense of who we are as a student and distinct us collectively as COLPHYSSITES.<br />\r\nI must also add that theres a need for us to discover and always consider what your core values are relating it to your everyday thoughts, actions and what we spend most of the time on to know if we really have to reframe our decisions and hold ourselves accountable. I believe SUCCESS IS WHAT EVERYONE CAN ATTAIN.</span></p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][kc_call_to_action layout=\"2\" title=\"Meet Your Exco:apos:s\" desc=\"V2UgYXJlIHlvdXIgcmVwcmVzZW50aXZlcywgc2Nyb2xsIGRvd24gdG8ga25vdyB5b3VyIGVsZWN0ZWQgZXhlY3V0aXZlcyBhbmQgbGVhcm4gbW9yZSBob3cgd2UgY2FuIHNlcnZlIHlvdSBiZXR0ZXIu\" button_show=\"yes\" button_text=\"Scroll Down\" _id=\"214726\" icon_show=\"yes\" icon=\"fa-angle-double-down\"][kc_spacing height=\"12px\" _id=\"111116\"][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_spacing height=\"42px\" _id=\"116134\"][/kc_column][/kc_row][kc_row use_container=\"yes\" _id=\"75272\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" force=\"yes\" parallax=\"yes\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`background`:{`background|`:``}}}}\"][kc_column width=\"50%\" video_mute=\"no\" _id=\"804196\"][kc_spacing height=\"42px\" _id=\"627959\"][kc_call_to_action layout=\"2\" title=\"ASSON Fresher/D.E Due Payment\