(1865, 1, '2021-10-19 23:32:25', '2021-10-19 23:32:25', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>GREATEST COLPHYSSITES </em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":1868,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost/colphyssa/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/colphyssa-news-1024x478.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1868\"/><figcaption><em>Colphyssa Executives Led By Comrade Saheed Akeye</em></figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All forms of praise and appreciation are bestowed onto the Almighty for this success. Its really a dream come true. And I must say, its been tremendous honor to attain this post, as the president of this prestigious student association(Colphys). Im so happy to be part of her history.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My appreciation in bulk and gross goes to the Dean, the Head Of Departments(HOD) and lecturers for been a great leader behind the curtain and a strong pillar for the college. Also, my special regards to the past executives of this great college for their relentless service and energy they have invested in this college, most especially the immediate tenure led by <strong>COMR.ONI JOSEPH</strong>. I really appreciate the Electoral Committee for the successful election and also appreciate the love and kind gesture that Colphyssite shown during the election.<br>Just so you know ,this is <strong>SYNERGY</strong>, everyones hands are needed to lift the glory of this great college. Team synergy is a blessing with lot of personalities and greatness ready to make Colphys a better place for us all. We will do our best to fufill our promises, as we are ready to give you nothing but the best.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cheers to greatness</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Signed;<br>Comr. Akeye Saheed <strong>AKEYE </strong><br><em>COLPHYSSA PRESIDENT</em><br>http://wa.me/2348181977807</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ANNOUNCER<br>Comr. Adebayo Zainab <strong>\" ZAINNY </strong><br><em>COLPHYSSA PRO 1</em><br>http://wa.me/2348106873614</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Comr. Yinusa Timothy \" <strong>TIMZY </strong><br>CO<em>LPHYSSA PRO 2</em><br>wa.me/2349152680072</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'THE PRESIDENTIAL INAUGURAL SPEECH', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-presidential-inaugural-speech', '', '', '2021-10-19 23:42:18', '2021-10-19 23:42:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/colphyssa/?p=1865', 0, 'post', '', 0),
